  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Add</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Allow large backups (greater than temp disk size)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Override license files</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span>Bugs</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Injecting an existing secret into a custom service via a new key was not injecting it with the expected key</li>\n<li>DXPC console was showing image versions of builds that fail to deploy</li>\n<li><span>If additional information was stored in the custom SSL, the certificate metadata was causing failed deployments</span></li>\n<li><span>Webserver endpoint was not coming up</span></li>\n<li><span>Created VPN was disappearing after connecting</span></li>\n<li><span>Deployment in progress was not finishing to deploy</span></li>\n<li><span>Wrong total time in autoscale report when not scaled</span></li>\n<li><span>Certificates were double-encoded when set via secrets</span></li>\n<li><span>Deploy status was keeping in progress indefinitely when pods in Terminating</span></li>\n</ul>"
      },
